            . I am a <rs id="t18191201-82-viclabel483" type="occupation">working silversmith</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191201-82-victim949 t18191201-82-viclabel483"></join>, and live in <placeName id="t18191201-82-crimeloc484">Bartholomew-close</placeName>
